    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/38fd09cc20850b0d72adf28fb602260e.poster.avif?t=1747581555\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/38fd09cc20850b0d72adf28fb602260e.webm?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/38fd09cc20850b0d72adf28fb602260e.mp4?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Fragile Reflection》是一款复古风格的第三人称生存恐怖游戏，背景设定于20世纪90年代末的日本，故事发生在一座被黑暗与秘密笼罩的神秘城市暗影之处。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >归家之途已然失控：村落被诡异能面扭曲，异界倒影正悄然渗透入我们的现实……  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜寻物品，解开谜团，与异形搏斗，穿梭于次元之间——协助伊藤佳莉绪揭开尘封的奥秘，在这款复古风格的生存恐怖游戏中求得生存！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/869a41645ffb7229336c747497f601e4.poster.avif?t=1747581555\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/869a41645ffb7229336c747497f601e4.webm?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/869a41645ffb7229336c747497f601e4.mp4?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情体验复古画面与现代操控系统的完美融合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作灵感汲取自经典生存恐怖游戏系列的美学意境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/09c9725719522d4bad2dcbe8d08f83c6.poster.avif?t=1747581555\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/09c9725719522d4bad2dcbe8d08f83c6.webm?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/09c9725719522d4bad2dcbe8d08f83c6.mp4?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着剧情推进，你将发掘一种超自然能力，使你得以在常世与倒影世界之间自如穿行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >倒影是一方保存着往昔痕迹的异世界。善用两个世界来解开谜题并寻觅真相！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/382a09b84c84432acbf2a47bfa24049f.poster.avif?t=1747581555\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/382a09b84c84432acbf2a47bfa24049f.webm?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/382a09b84c84432acbf2a47bfa24049f.mp4?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村庄中发生了骇人听闻之事——这些诡异生物从何而来？可否终结这场噩梦？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协助女主角在这恐怖现实中存活并寻找她的双亲。探索日本南苦乐市，解开谜团，妥善管理弹药，巧妙利用环境助你一臂之力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/da5c204a22c4aa5ce115d3fe2bf264d7.poster.avif?t=1747581555\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/da5c204a22c4aa5ce115d3fe2bf264d7.webm?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111440/extras/da5c204a22c4aa5ce115d3fe2bf264d7.mp4?t=1747581555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接到当地医院一通令人不安的电话后，伊藤佳莉绪立即前往她的故乡南苦乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女主角将不得不揭开多年来对她隐瞒的一切真相，并在与佩戴传统日本能乐面具的诡异怪物抗争的同时求得生存，这些面具承载着历史、象征意义和某种神秘力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村庄正被倒影世界所吞噬，这是一个平行次元，保存着曾在这片神圣土地上生活过的人们留下的往事、情感和心绪的碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若连自己的倒影都无法展现全部真相，佳莉绪最终能相信任何人吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>次元穿梭</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  运用超自然能力解开谜团并揭示真相</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复古美学</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  画面与氛围灵感源自经典恐怖主机游戏</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索与叙事</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  探索一座被神秘生物、奇诡事件和诅咒传闻所笼罩的矿业村落</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>声效与音乐</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 原创配乐融合旅行嘻哈、氛围、心灵之旅风格，灵感汲取自山冈晃的音乐作品</p>",
